			<div class="post-box">
					<article class="post-220 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blog tag-cyanogen-rom" id="post-220">
		<header>
        	<time class="updated" datetime="2009-08-28T06:24:18+00:00" pubdate>August 28th, 2009 &bull; Written by <a href="http://www.cyanogenmod.org/author/cyanogen" rel="author" class="fn">Steve Kondik</a></time>        	<h2 class="entry-title">CyanogenMod 4.0.3.1 is out!</h2>
					</header>
		<div class="entry-content">
			<p>This is a small upgrade for the stable series that contains new bluetooth and audio code backported from Donut, as well as some kernel changes which should improve responsiveness.  Get it with CM Updater!</p>
		</div>

